Constructor Detail

TextArea

public TextArea(java.lang.String text)
Constructor for the plain text area that is initialized to the given text string. This class uses a JTextArea to model the text panel in the application. This text area uses a single font and marks lines for type by using specific characters in certain positions.

Parameters:
text - intializing text for the text area
